<Layout
  description="Everything we have learned integrating Stripe across SaaS apps — Checkout, webhooks, subscription gotchas, test mode traps, and the invoice bug that cost us a weekend."
  title="Everything We've Learned About Integrating Stripe (After Breaking It Several Times) · Blog · Aidxn Design"
>

    <SlotBlog>
      <Fragment slot="category">
        Payments &amp; SaaS
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Everything We've Learned About Integrating Stripe (After Breaking It Several Times)
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <div class="w-full h-48 rounded bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600/20 to-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
